    "content": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><head></head><body class=\"tei-surface3\" id=\"srcD_surface_a3v\"><div class=\"content \"><pb-facs-link emit=\"transcription\" facs=\"https://ores.klassik-stiftung.de/digilib/Scaler/IIIF/gsa!Arbeitskopie!71!75094!75094_6\" style=\"float: right; margin-top: -2em;\">a3v</pb-facs-link><div id=\"srcD_surface_a3v\" class=\"transkriptionField\" style=\"\"><div id=\"srcD_zone_a3v_div2_d2e48\" style=\"padding-top:10em;\" class=\"firstBlock textBlock \" debug-msg=\"test\" data-debug=\"1\"><div id=\"srcD_zone_a3v_fw_d2e26\" class=\"fw-top-right\" style=\"left:49.4083em;top:2.025em;\"><span class=\"tei-fw2\"><span id=\"a3v_fw_d2e26\" class=\"top-right hand N_red\"><span class=\"inline   \">VI. </span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l6l5l5l5l6\" class=\"hatching\">VII</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l6l5l5l5l6\"><span class=\"transcription\">VII</span></pb-popover></span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"a3v_fw_d2e26\"><p><span style=\"font-style: italic;\"><pb-i18n key=\"myapp.hand.N_red\">\n                            key not found: myapp.hand.N_red</pb-i18n></span><span style=\"font-style: italic;\">\n                         ( <pb-i18n key=\"myapp.hatching\">\n                            key not found: </pb-i18n>)</span></p></pb-popover></span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb1\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb1\" duration=\"5000\">1</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">als „den Bösen“ anzusetzen, höherwerthig im Sinn der Förderung, Nützlichkeit, Gedeihlichkeit in Hinsicht auf <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">den</span> Menschen über-\n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb2\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb2\" duration=\"5000\">2</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">haupt (die Zukunft des Menschen eingerechnet) Wie<pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"a3v_add_d2e66\" style=\"\"><p><span style=\"font-style: italic;\"><pb-i18n key=\"myapp.overwritten\">\n                            überschrieben\n                          </pb-i18n>:</span><span class=\"transkriptionField small \"><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l6l5l7l5l3\" class=\"strikethrough\">,</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l6l5l7l5l3\"><span class=\"transcription\">,</span></pb-popover></span></p></pb-popover><span class=\"trigger popover\" id=\"a3v_add_d2e66\" data-debug=\"add4\"><span class=\"inline  \">?</span></span> wenn das Umgekehrte die Wahrheit wäre? Wie? wenn im „Guten“ \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb3\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb3\" duration=\"5000\">3</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">auch ein Rückgangssymptom läge, insgleichen eine Gefahr, eine Verführung, ein Gift, ein <span class=\"latin\">Narcoticum</span>, durch das \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb4\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb4\" duration=\"5000\">4</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">etwa die Gegenwart <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">auf</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Kosten</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">der</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Zukunft</span> lebte? Vielleicht behaglicher, ungefährlicher, aber auch in kleinerem Stile, \n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb5\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb5\" duration=\"5000\">5</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">niedriger?… So daß gerade die Moral daran Schuld wäre, wenn eine an sich mögliche <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">höchste</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Mächtigkeit</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">und</span>\n               </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb6\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb6\" duration=\"5000\">6</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Pracht</span> des Typus Mensch niemals erreicht würde?… So daß gerade die Moral die Gefahr der Gefahren wäre?…\n             \n            \n               \n                  </span></div></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_a3v_div2_GMVorrede07\" style=\"padding-bottom:22em;padding-top:3em;\" class=\"lastBlock textBlock \" debug-msg=\"test\" data-debug=\"1\"><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_head_d2e110_a3v_lb7\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb7\" duration=\"5000\">7</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span id=\"srcD_zone_a3v_head_d2e110_a3v_lb7\" style=\"margin-left:22.3em;\" class=\"head\" data-debug=\"0\">7.\n               \n                  </span></span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb8\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb8\" duration=\"5000\">8</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" indent\" style=\"\">Genug, daß <span class=\"insertionMark right  insertion-above \" style=\"top:0em;height:1.3125em;\" debug-msg=\"2\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"left:0.3em;\">ich</span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l6l7\" class=\"hatching\">mir</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l6l7\"><span class=\"transcription\">mir</span></pb-popover> selbst, seitdem mir dieser Ausblick sich öffnete, Gründe hatte, mich nach gelehrten, kühnen und arbeit-\n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb9\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb9\" duration=\"5000\">9</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">samen Genossen umzusehn (ich thue es heute noch). Es gilt, das ungeheure, ferne und so versteckte Land der Moral – \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb10\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb10\" duration=\"5000\">10</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">der wirklich dagewesenen, wirklich gelebten Moral – mit lauter neuen Fragen und gleichsam mit neuen Augen zu \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb11\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb11\" duration=\"5000\">11</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">bereisen: und heißt dies nicht beinahe so viel als dieses Land erst <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">entdecken</span>?… Wenn ich dabei, unter Anderen, \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb12\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb12\" duration=\"5000\">12</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">auch an den genannten <span class=\"latin\">Dr. Rée</span> dachte, so geschah es, weil ich gar nicht zweifelte, daß er von der Natur seiner Fra-\n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb13\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb13\" duration=\"5000\">13</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">gen selbst auf eine richtigere Methodik, um zu Antworten zu gelangen, gedrängt werden würde. Habe ich mich darin \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb14\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb14\" duration=\"5000\">14</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">betrogen? Mein Wunsch war es jedenfalls, einem so scharfen und unbetheiligten Auge eine bessere Richtung, die Rich-\n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb15\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb15\" duration=\"5000\">15</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">tung zur wirklichen <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Historie</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">der</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Moral</span> zu geben und ihn vor solchem englischen Hypothesenwesen <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">ins</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Blaue</span>  \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb16\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb16\" duration=\"5000\">16</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">noch zur rechten Zeit zu warnen. Es liegt ja auf der Hand, welche Farbe für einen Moral-Genealogen hundert \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb17\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb17\" duration=\"5000\">17</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">Mal wichtiger sein muß als gerade das Blaue: nämlich <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">das</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Graue</span>, will sagen, das Urkundliche, das Wirklich-\n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb18\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb18\" duration=\"5000\">18</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">Feststellbare, das Wirklich-Dagewesene, kurz die ganze lange schwer zu entziffernde Hieroglyphenschrift der \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb19\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb19\" duration=\"5000\">19</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">menschlichen Moral-Vergangenheit! – <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Diese</span> war dem <span class=\"latin\">Dr. Rée</span> unbekannt; aber er hatte Darwin gelesen – und \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb20\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb20\" duration=\"5000\">20</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">so reichen sich in seinen Hypothesen auf eine Weise, die zum Mindesten unterhaltend ist, die Darwinsche Bestie \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb21\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb21\" duration=\"5000\">21</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">und der allermodernste <span class=\"insertion-below hand typesetter_black1\"><span class=\"below \" style=\"left:-0.6em;top:0.3em;\"><pb-highlight key=\"#mark1a_a3v#mark1b_a3v\" highlight-self=\"highlight-self\" duration=\"5000\">⌊</pb-highlight></span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l19l6\" class=\"strikethrough-typesetter_black1\">kleinbürgerliche</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l19l6\"><span class=\"transcription\">kleinbürgerliche</span></pb-popover> <span class=\"insertion-above hand typesetter_black1\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"left:-0.9em;top:-1.4em;\"><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l19l8l5\" class=\"strikethrough-typesetter_black1\">Genüßling</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l19l8l5\"><span class=\"transcription\">Genüßling</span></pb-popover></span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l19l9\" class=\"strikethrough-typesetter_black1\">Zärtling</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l19l9\"><span class=\"transcription\">Zärtling</span></pb-popover> und <span class=\"insertion-above hand typesetter_black1\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"left:1em;top:-1.4em;\"><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l19l11l5\" class=\"strikethrough-typesetter_black1\">Stubenhocker</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l19l11l5\"><span class=\"transcription\">Stubenhocker</span></pb-popover></span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l19l12\" class=\"strikethrough-typesetter_black1\">Bildungsphilister</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l19l12\"><span class=\"transcription\">Bildungsphilister</span></pb-popover> artig die Hand, letzterer mit dem Ausdruck \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb22\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb22\" duration=\"5000\">22</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">einer gewissen gutmüthigen und feinen Indolenz im Gesicht, in die selbst ein Gran von Pessimismus, von Ermü-\n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb23\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb23\" duration=\"5000\">23</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">dung eingemischt ist: als ob es sich eigentlich gar nicht lohne, alle diese Dinge – die Probleme der Moral <span class=\"inline   \">–</span> so \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb24\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb24\" duration=\"5000\">24</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">ernst zu nehmen. Mir nun scheint es umgekehrt gar keine Dinge zu geben, die es mehr <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">lohnten</span>, daß man \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb25\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb25\" duration=\"5000\">25</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">sie ernst nimmt; zu welchem Lohne es zum Beispiel gehört, daß man eines Tags vielleicht die Erlaub-\n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb26\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb26\" duration=\"5000\">26</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">niß erhält, sie <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">heiter</span> zu nehmen. Die Heiterkeit nämlich oder, um es in meiner Sprache zu sagen, <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">die</span> \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb27\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb27\" duration=\"5000\">27</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\"><span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">fröhliche</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Wissenschaft</span> – ist ein Lohn: ein Lohn für einen langen, tapferen, arbeitsamen <span id=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l25l8\" class=\"hatching\">Ernst</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l25l8\"><span class=\"transcription\">Ernst</span></pb-popover> und unter-\n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb28\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb28\" duration=\"5000\">28</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">irdischen Ernst, der freilich nicht Jedermanns Sache ist. An dem Tage aber, wo wir aus vollem Herzen \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb29\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb29\" duration=\"5000\">29</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">sagen: „vorwärts! auch unsre alte Moral gehört <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">in</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">die</span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Komödie</span>!“ haben wir für das <span class=\"insertion-above hand Koeselitz_pencil\"><span class=\"above \" style=\"left:-0.421875em;top:-1.4em;\">dionysische</span></span><span id=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l27l12\" class=\"strikethrough-Koeselitz_pencil\">hundertaktige</span><pb-popover theme=\"material\" for=\"PD43107N2l9l6l6l27l12\"><span class=\"transcription\">hundertaktige</span></pb-popover> Dra-\n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb30\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb30\" duration=\"5000\">30</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">ma vom „Schicksal der Seele“ eine neue Verwicklung und Möglichkeit entdeckt –: und er wird sie sich \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb31\" class=\"line\" style=\"\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb31\" duration=\"5000\">31</pb-highlight></span><span class=\" \" style=\"\">schon zu Nutze machen, darauf darf man wetten, er, der große alte ewige Komödiendichter unsres Daseins!…\n               \n                  </span></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_a3v_ab_d2e296_a3v_lb32\" class=\"ab-zone\"><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb32\" class=\"zoneLine\" style=\"bottom:13.8625em;\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb32\" duration=\"5000\">32</pb-highlight></span><span class=\"marginLeft  \" style=\"margin-left:3em;\"><span class=\"latin\"><span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Sils</span>-<span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\">Maria</span></span>, Oberengadin,\n                  </span></div></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_a3v_ab_d2e296_a3v_lb33\" class=\"ab-zone\"><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb33\" class=\"zoneLine\" style=\"bottom:10.8625em;\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb33\" duration=\"5000\">33</pb-highlight></span><span class=\"marginLeft  \" style=\"margin-left:4.7em;\">im Juli 1887.\n               \n                  \n                     </span></div></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_a3v_ab_d2e309_a3v_lb34\" class=\"ab-zone\"><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_lb34\" class=\"zoneLine\" style=\"bottom:4.08125em;\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb34\" duration=\"5000\">34</pb-highlight></span><span class=\"marginLeft  \" style=\"margin-left:2.18752em;\"><span class=\"inline  hand typesetter_black1 \"><span class=\"inline instantaneous hand typesetter_black1 \"><pb-highlight key=\"#mark1a_a3v#mark1b_a3v\" highlight-self=\"highlight-self\" duration=\"5000\">⌊</pb-highlight></span> bescheidene Moral-Zärtling, der „nicht mehr beißt“</span>\n            \n            \n               \n               </span></div></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_a3v_note_d2e320_a3v_lb35\" class=\"note-zone\"><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_note_d2e320_a3v_lb35\" class=\"zoneLine\" style=\"bottom:12.3625em;\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb35\" duration=\"5000\">35</pb-highlight></span><span class=\"marginLeft hand N_brown1 \" style=\"margin-left:23.375em;\">NB! Hierauf folgt ein leeres Blatt, auf dem nur diese Wor-\n               </span></div></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_a3v_note_d2e320_a3v_lb36\" class=\"note-zone\"><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_note_d2e320_a3v_lb36\" class=\"zoneLine\" style=\"bottom:8.3625em;\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb36\" duration=\"5000\">36</pb-highlight></span><span class=\"marginLeft hand N_brown1 \" style=\"margin-left:23.375em;\">te stehn: \n               </span></div></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_a3v_note_d2e320_a3v_lb37\" class=\"note-zone\"><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_note_d2e320_a3v_lb37\" class=\"zoneLine\" style=\"bottom:6.3625em;\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb37\" duration=\"5000\">37</pb-highlight></span><span class=\"marginLeft hand N_brown1 \" style=\"margin-left:28.75em;\"><span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\"><span class=\"latin\">Erste</span></span> <span class=\"tei-hi2 underline\"><span class=\"latin\">Abhandlung</span></span><span class=\"latin\">: \n               </span></span></div></div><div id=\"srcD_zone_a3v_note_d2e320_a3v_lb38\" class=\"note-zone\"><div id=\"srcD_line_a3v_note_d2e320_a3v_lb38\" class=\"zoneLine\" style=\"bottom:3.3625em;\"><span class=\"lnr\"><pb-highlight key=\"a3v_lb38\" duration=\"5000\">38</pb-highlight></span><span class=\"marginLeft hand N_brown1 \" style=\"margin-left:26.75em;\"><span class=\"latin\">„Gut und Böse“, „Gut und Schlecht.“</span></span></div></div></div></div></div></body></html>",
